result.name: Ko Lau Wan Seafood Hot Pot Restaurant

reviews.text: Terrific and specialty seafood and beef hotpot that you cant find elsewhere. Warm and nice staff
Not only is the food amazing and fairly priced, the service is awesome too. Quite simply the best food we’ve had in Hong Kong!

Been here so many times. Consistently good service and fresh food

Back again...different crowd but same good quality food and service

Authentic Chinese hotpot. Frequented mainly by mainland Chinese, while I was there, which was a good thing. The soup stock was very flavorful,  we just added the various ingredients. A very satisfying meal.

If one wanna go for steamboat in Hong Kong, this is definitely one of if not the place to go. Their mixed seafood platter is quite good but would recommend to order ala carte. Their soup base is nucely done and I don3think any MSG is used. One oh the side dish i recommend is their deep fried chinese style churro (or "yao tiu" ala "yao ja kwai" in cantonese)- stuffed with fish paste and topped with generoys amount of fish roe, this is my favourite. Depending on what you order, our bill for 5 pax with a few bottles of beer and drinks costs about HKD2,000.00.

result.name: 高流灣海鮮火鍋酒家

reviews.text: 好新鮮的田雞腿上枱的時候還在跳動👍
一貫水準👍🏼

제 유튜브 리뷰에 종종 등장하는 고류완!
이곳은 다른 훠궈 집에 비해서 가격대가 조금 있는 편이지만,
홍콩에 갈때마다 즐겨가는 맛집 중 한 곳입니다. (현지사람들이 주로 가는 곳이라 한국인들에게 많이 알려지지 않은 음식점!) 소고기가 다른 집에 비해 신선하고 훠궈에서 제일 중요한게 찍어 먹는 소스의 맛과 육수 인데, 이곳의 소스는 한국인들의 입맛에 잘 맞는 소스라고 생각합니다! 저 또한 강한 향신료가 들어간 음식을 못먹는 사람 중 하나인데, 이곳 백탕과 소스는 맛이 강하지 않고 한국인들이 먹었을때 전혀 거부감 없는 맛입니다.(백탕,홍탕 모두다 맛있어요.)저는 주로 소고기와 닭을 주문해서 먹습니다~랍스터 회랑 새우 회도 맛있었어요!
그리고 마지막에 우동면 꼭 시켜서 먹으세요!!!!되게 쫄깃하고 맛있어요 칼국수면 느낌인데, 백탕에 담궜다 익으면 건져서 만들어둔 훠궈 소스에 비벼서 먹으면 진짜 맛있어요!
———————————————————————
I think the hotpot of this restaurant is very delicious. The beef in this restaurant is very fresh and the seafood is also delicious. And hotpot sauce tastes good, too. The staff is also kind, so I often go to this restaurant.
食左兩啖牛就打打下邊停電  人生第一次
好食新鮮。。但要記得訂位呀
